snippet.title: Akhena: Age of Evil Early Access Gameplay
snippet.description:
The first hour of gameplay as a Brinhar Mercenary in the Aeland Kingdom. Together with your childhood friend Sébastien you venture forth into the coastal kingdom from your home town Banodon, in search of a magik crystal and forbidden knowledge.

Akhena: Age of Evil is available on Steam
